---
title: Miso Corn Fritters & Sesame Fries with Mixed Asian Salad & Roasted Peanuts
description: This plate of veggie-loaded miso fritters is so packed with bountiful flavour, you’ll be hard-pressed on what to start eating first. Enjoy the crunch that comes from the Asian-style salad and the moreish miso dressing slathered over the fritters and sesame fries.

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
